asset.title: adidas Skateboarding Superstar ADV
asset.description:
True style is developed in the streets and redefined by each generation. The freshest adidas ambassadors carry a 90s skateboarding staple into the present, exploring the grit and grime of Tyshawn Jones’ homecourt of NYC and sun bleached spots of Miami in the new Superstar ADV. Tyshawn Jones, Chewy Cannon, Benny Fairfax, Raul Navarro, and Miles Silvas navigate the streets and day-to-day living of these cultural hubs as only they can.
